Package: feventr
Type: Package
Title: Causal Inference for Financial Event Studies
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Paul", "Goldsmith-Pinkham", email = "paulgp@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Estimators for causal inference in financial event studies,
    implementing the methods studied in Goldsmith-Pinkham and Lyu, "Causal
    Inference in Financial Event Studies": difference baselines, factor-model
    abnormal returns, fast synthetic control (Frank-Wolfe with support-restricted
    QP polish), ridge-augmented synthetic control, synthetic
    difference-in-differences, and generalized synthetic control, with a common
    panel input and fit object across single-event and many-event batch modes.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports: data.table, osqp, parallel, stats, utils
